1/* $NetBSD: familyname.c,v 1.1.1.1 2012/03/23 21:20:08 christos Exp $ */
2
3#include "ipf.h"
4
5const char *familyname(int family)
6{
7 if (family == AF_INET)
8 return "inet";
9#ifdef AF_INET6
10 if (family == AF_INET6)
11 return "inet6";
12#endif
13 return "unknown";
14}
